I"0<h1 id="概述">概述</h1>

<p>工作中经常会将Linux输出进行格式化，方便阅读。本文罗列几个常用的将输出转换为Json格式的方法。</p>

<h1 id="实践">实践</h1>

<h2 id="方法1-python--mjsontool">方法1 ‘python -mjson.tool’</h2>

<p>此适用于多种OS</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">ceph config-key get gateway_groups | python -mjson.tool</code></p>

<h2 id="方法2-json_pp-or-jq">方法2 ‘json_pp’ or ‘jq’</h2>

<p>适用于Debin系OS</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">ceph config-key get gateway_groups | json_pp</code></p>

<p>适用于RedHat系OS，带颜色</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">ceph config-key get gateway_groups | jq</code></p>

<p>e.g:</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>root@CVM01:~# ceph config-key get gateway_groups | json_pp
obtained 'gateway_groups'
{
   "groups" : {
      "Default" : {
         "member" : [
            "10.10.101.102",
            "10.10.101.103",
            "10.10.101.101",
            "10.10.101.104"
         ],
         "type" : "standard",
         "zerocopy" : false
      },
      "!!!not used!!!" : {
         "type" : "standard",
         "member" : []
      }
   },
   "virtual_gateways" : {},
   "_ver" : "5.2"
}
</code></pre></div></div>

